_sText: A new dusty map for nice and clean game play. It has 2 mostly same looking sides for CT's and T's. Just to give you a bit info about it: - 48 spawn points - 3d skybox - Indoors - Outdoors - Dusty look - A random earthquake to shake the ground slightly - Dust soundscape > To install the map, put the new cstrike folder over your old one and ever write. Hope you enjoy the map. Rating, commenting, advising is more then welcome! Enjoy! :D
